name: LIAR'S MASK
description:
MÁSCARAS #2 LIAR'S MASK


this mask represents the energy of insecurity, always 
lying to your self to find the excuses you need, as you were building hair thin walls of distractions and distortions.


3D modeling by OBU and oburaco.
Analog textures developed by ZALA, with spray NOU and acrylic on paper.
